Package: nightvale
Type: Package
Title: Access Welcome to Night Vale Proverbs
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Luke", "McGuinness",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "luke.mcguinness@bristol.ac.uk"))
Description: Welcome to Night Vale is a podcast is a twice-monthly podcast in
    the style of community updates for the small desert town of Night Vale, with
    heavy themes of surreal humor and horror. A key and recurring part of the 
    show is "Today's Proverb". This package provides the metadata and proverb 
    for each episode as a dataset, in addition to a function to return a nicely 
    formatted proverb to the console.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/mcguinlu/nightvale
BugReports: https://github.com/mcguinlu/nightvale/issues
